    "// PID-CONFLICT-NOTE TS0505B shared with 19 other drivers (cross-class; mfrs distinct (false positive)). Sacred Couple rule applies: mfr+PID pair disambiguates. See: docs/P2_PID_CONFLICT_RESOLUTION_2026-07-12.md",
    "// PID-CONFLICT-NOTE TS0505A shared with 13 other drivers (cross-class; mfrs distinct (false positive)). Sacred Couple rule applies: mfr+PID pair disambiguates. See: docs/P2_PID_CONFLICT_RESOLUTION_2026-07-12.md"
  ]
}
